Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During this age where Tokyo was submerged
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,due to a change in the earth's crust,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are professionals who specialize in collecting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,companies' secrets and national treasures
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that disappeared into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are called the Salvagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika Sumeragi is one of the prettiest amongst the Salvagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I, Rion Aida, am her pretty assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Neina, who controls the army of pretty girls called the Delmogeny,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stands against our K2 corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind her was the conspiracy planned by her brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rudolph Hargen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a crazy plan of trying to wipe out humankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the power of the mysterious Raggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to that plan, we faced a series of difficulties.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in a mad deficit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was finally settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I am going to pull together our K2 Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make it really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:43.80,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to become a lost sheep with frightened eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:50.17,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though my heart has no room to trust something or save someone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:57.55,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when things change when I go against my destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:04.15,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:09.28,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if tomorrow carries the cross of yesterday and continues to grieve
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.39,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I try to find the meaning of life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:15.73,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,And just capriciously recite justice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:23.17,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to blindfold the depression and start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:29.78,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the time I take back the glory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:33.11,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The distress of the blue world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:36.15,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The skyscraper in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:39.19,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I sleep by holding the sin and punishment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:42.52,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,After my dream and freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:48.86,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to not repeat the broken tenderness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:55.20,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the words the wind whispers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:59.44,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,And begin tomorrow once again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aika, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.51,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,143)}Moving
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, looking at an old promotional video?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our company used to profit a lot during these days, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to make cool videos like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were those times too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting that aside, stop fooling around and help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should let the newcomer help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, he's Michitaro Michikusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:50.50,Resume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz31.427\pos(104,126)}Resume
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shuntaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I saw him on a magazine that my brother used to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have him take a picture with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can you take a picture with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that slow, the sun's going to set!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, youngsters these days won't do anything unless they're told!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it is a lease, we were finally able
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to get an office building for our K2 Corporation.
