Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:24.29,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're completely part of me, I don't want to hold back anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:28.31,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember, we got GD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.86,English,,0000,0000,0000,,If curiosity moves in the point of the compass
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:34.73,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Then most likely the special power will arise
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:39.00,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent city, we're salvager
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:45.67,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I will one day find the skyscraper of the submerged city
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:49.84,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid, come together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:06:00.45,English,,0000,0000,0000,,By passing through time, let's revive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:12.37,English,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things that the sun shines upon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:15.04,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:23.38,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to convey it to you, I don't want you to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.88,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I take you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:33.92,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Since there is a world awaiting that no one has ever seen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.48,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.99,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Always
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:05.41,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave the noisy city
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:15.93,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get rid of the boots and walk with the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:21.53,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,By taking a deep breath in and out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:31.41,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The innocent feeling that I forgot awakened
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:46.68,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,If I rest my chin on my hand near the moon window, I think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:55.74,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Until yesterday, I was pretending not to notice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:08:02.88,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that I was hiding deep down in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:11.55,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I am more pure than I appear to be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:21.89,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always caught in between toughness and shyness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:31.54,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of the shining city
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:41.74,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,The sounds were erased by the sounds of the bells and honks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.95,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember that day's heartbeat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:57.49,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,And the fingertips that I felt were very sad
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:13.15,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,If I count the stars and sigh, you overflow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:21.66,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Since more strong feelings are forming little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:28.86,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow it's going to be a new me
